<taxonomicName box="[662,789,1807,1831]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Salicaceae" genus="Homalium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="24" pageNumber="255" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="baillonii">
<emphasis box="[662,789,1807,1831]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="255">H. baillonii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
should be resurrected for two of these.
</paragraph>
